CHANGES
=======

0.1.0 (Unreleased)
------------------

* Initial project specification and documentation
* Added README.md with project overview
* Added QUICKSTART.md with getting started guide
* Added ARCHITECTURE.md with system design
* Added DESIGN.md with design decisions and rationale
* Added CONTRIBUTING.md with contribution guidelines
* Added API.md with library API reference
* Added dual MIT/GPL-3.0 license
* Set up pbr for build and version management
* Set up Pipenv for dependency management
* Implemented the complete ``casconf`` Python package:

  * ``casconf.api`` — ``merge_configs()`` public entry point
  * ``casconf.cli`` — ``argparse``-based CLI (``casconf`` command)
  * ``casconf.discovery`` — ``DiscoveryConfig`` and directory scanner
  * ``casconf.merger`` — deep and shallow merge strategies
  * ``casconf.parser`` — extension-based format detection with fallback chain
  * ``casconf.registry`` — pluggable parser/writer registry
  * ``casconf.writer`` — serialise to JSON, YAML, or TOML
  * ``casconf.exceptions`` — typed exception hierarchy
  * ``casconf.__main__`` — ``python -m casconf`` support
  * ``py.typed`` marker for PEP 561 inline type information

* Added 99 unit tests across 7 test modules; coverage threshold set to 90%
* Made ``pyyaml`` and ``tomli-w``/``tomli`` optional package extras (``casconf[yaml]`` and ``casconf[toml]``)
